title: Is Trump bringing us to war? (Re-cap)
description:

Today I make my triumphant return to youtube, re-capping and explaining what I've missed since I've been away. Let's just say it's been a lot in the realm of foreign policy, as president Trump has bombed a Syrian airstrip, and dropped the mother of all bombs on an ISIS stronghold in Afghanistan. In this video I discuss both the literal, and political fallout of these two events, while of course pointing out the silly reaction of some in the media.
